--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
 Naggy Raid: OP ORDER<br>
<br>
Situation: The Guild Alliance will attack the Dragon known as Nagafen (if not killed earlier in the week, if so, see Appendix A). This raid will be in support of the Avengers Federation Second Anniversary and Yumdaien Elliscers Epic Weapon Quest item the , Book of Scales.<br>
<br>
Mission: On the 19th of May at 10:00am EST the Guild Alliance meet at the druid ring in Lavastorm Mountains and will destroy the Dragon known as Nagafen located in Nagafens Lair aka SolB. In order to acquire the Book of Scales for Yumdaien Elliscer 52 Paladin of the Avengers Federation. <br>
Execution<br>
        <br>
Intent: Kill the dragon while receiving minimal deaths and acquire the Book of Scale for Yumdaien Elliscer. Also acquiring phat loot for the Alliance of Guilds and better prepare our Alliance for future dragon raids.<br>
        <br>
Concept of operation: Move quickly through the Fire Giants, buff up and kill Naggy. <br>
1. Largest Meatshield pulls Nags close to the door.<br>
2. Rest of the tanks run BEHIND Nagafen so that he is always facing the door.<br>
3. Tanks keep Naggy AWAY from the lava at all times! No melee should be attacking at his sides.<br>
4. Have a suicidal enchanter to take a death from Tashing Nagefen. Volunteers?<br>
5. At 60, nukers run in and stand on Naggy's tail, then chain IC(wiz) and ice(druids). Forgot what mages cast.<br>
<br>
<br>
Characters needed: If we do not receive enough of the classes needed we will begin to make it open to all classes one week prior.<br>
<br>
